1779
01:46:41,220 --> 01:46:44,650
The question is, what are
the trade offs and then

1780
01:46:44,650 --> 01:46:45,990
which one is used in practice?

1781
01:46:45,990 --> 01:46:49,770
So I think it all depends on
your compute budget, on how much

1782
01:46:49,770 --> 01:46:54,450
