1788
01:47:12,810 --> 01:47:16,470
is shown to show good results,
but maybe not the best results,

1789
01:47:16,470 --> 01:47:19,770
then DPO is your friend.

1790
01:47:19,770 --> 01:47:22,873
And if you're an expert
