1791
01:47:22,873 --> 01:47:24,290
you know what
you're doing and you

1792
01:47:24,290 --> 01:47:26,990
want the every last
bit of performance,

1793
01:47:26,990 --> 01:47:29,870
then PPO might be a better way.

1794
01:47:32,590 --> 01:47:33,230
Amazing.

1795
01:47:33,230 --> 01:47:36,800
And with that,
